metadata.name: 3 Millionaires
metadata.description: 1st Winner will be from 3 Millionaires NFT holder #1 - #100,000. 2nd winner will be chosen from 3 Millionaires NFT holder #100,001 #1,000,000. Millionaires will be announced via a live lucky draw when all 1,000,000 NFTs are minted. The holders of this collection will be included in next collection's lucky draw so this collection will always matter
